te\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jocelyn_Swyft&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Cersei I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc7.7